  <h2>Count Your Missed Calls This Week</h2>

  <p>Here's a challenge. This week, write down every missed call. Just look at your phone's call history each evening and count the ones you didn't answer. At the end of the week, do the maths.</p>

  <p>Then ask yourself: <strong>how long are you willing to keep losing this money?</strong></p>

